            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="whats-new">What's New<a href="https://quiz-flow-docs.netlify.app/blog/changelog-2026-02#whats-new" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to What's New" title="Direct link to What's New" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="flipcard-component-ccf-29">Flipcard Component (CCF-29)<a href="https://quiz-flow-docs.netlify.app/blog/changelog-2026-02#flipcard-component-ccf-29" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Flipcard Component (CCF-29)" title="Direct link to Flipcard Component (CCF-29)" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>Interactive flashcard component for learning and revision.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="drag-pieces-ccf-30">Drag Pieces (CCF-30)<a href="https://quiz-flow-docs.netlify.app/blog/changelog-2026-02#drag-pieces-ccf-30" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Drag Pieces (CCF-30)" title="Direct link to Drag Pieces (CCF-30)" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>Drag-and-drop puzzle interface for categorizing items.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="breathing-animation-ccf-44">Breathing Animation (CCF-44)<a href="https://quiz-flow-docs.netlify.app/blog/changelog-2026-02#breathing-animation-ccf-44" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Breathing Animation (CCF-44)" title="Direct link to Breathing Animation (CCF-44)" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>New <code>/breath</code> route with calming breathing exercises.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="categorization-puzzle-grid-ccf-39">Categorization Puzzle Grid (CCF-39)<a href="https://quiz-flow-docs.netlify.app/blog/changelog-2026-02#categorization-puzzle-grid-ccf-39" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Categorization Puzzle Grid (CCF-39)" title="Direct link to Categorization Puzzle Grid (CCF-39)" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>Section 5 now includes an interactive puzzle grid.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes<a href="https://quiz-flow-docs.netlify.app/blog/changelog-2026-02#bug-fixes" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Bug Fixes" title="Direct link to Bug Fixes" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">Restored polished drag-pieces design</li>
<li class="">Fixed EC2 config files</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="documentation">Documentation<a href="https://quiz-flow-docs.netlify.app/blog/changelog-2026-02#documentation" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Documentation" title="Direct link to Documentation" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">Complete rewrite of README</li>
<li class="">Updated architecture and setup guides</li>
<li class="">Added git commit guide</li>
</ul>]]></content:encoded>
